{"id": "1512314902478454906", "channel_id": "1512035381510406325", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello, really sorry to let our Korean players down<:Nymphaea_frustrated:1459078117485445288> .\n\nWhen we tried producing content in Chinese, English, and Korean at the same time, we found out that with our current team size we just can't keep it up reliably.\n\nOnce the timing's right, we'll get back to putting out content in other languages.<:ryker_pray:1468258632205340820> \n\n<@256852230685196288> <@422766128826417152>", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T04:39:30.203000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["256852230685196288", "422766128826417152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512035381510406325", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🎧 V2.5.1 广播剧《信使》┊Radio Drama - Messenger", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1512315225905430578", "channel_id": "1512035381510406325", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "The game will include a Korean-subtitled audio drama.<:Horla_Sendflowers:1468259514091573350>", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T04:40:47.314000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-05T06:07:24.152000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512035381510406325", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🎧 V2.5.1 广播剧《信使》┊Radio Drama - Messenger", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
{"id": "1512356641578684496", "channel_id": "1512035381510406325", "type": 19, "author_id": "422766128826417152", "author_name": "blackdonut5182", "author_bot": false, "content": "Korean users fully understand the situation you are in to some extent.\n\nWe look forward to your continued development of great games and are rooting for you.\n\nPlease just pay attention to the in-game translation issues. We are receiving many questions from people trying to get into this game asking if the translation problems have been resolved.\n\nI am not saying this to rush or pressure you, so please take it with good intentions.\n\nI am very happy that recently, the number of users in Korea who like this game and want to play it is increasing.", "timestamp": "2026-06-05T07:25:21.580000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-05T07:30:15.537000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1485258210209435701"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1512314902478454906", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1512035381510406325", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🎧 V2.5.1 广播剧《信使》┊Radio Drama - Messenger", "forum_channel_id": "1355085076500578363", "thread_tags": ["1356827958647586947", "1356828359543226469"]}
